    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on how Hayek's idea of the 'knowledge problem' applies to internet regulation? Like, how does the government's lack of knowledge make their attempts at regulation inherently harmful to free expression?",
      "source": "evaluator"
